The '''Golden Disk Awards''' is a awards show founded in 1986 that is presented annually by the Music Industry Association of Korea for outstanding achievements in the [[music industry]] in [[South Korea]].<ref>{{cite web |title=<U+ACE8><U+B4E0> <U+B514><U+C2A4><U+D06C> <U+C0C1> |url=http://isplus.joins.com/goldendisk |publisher=Golden Disk Awards |language=Korean |accessdate=2009-07-16}}</ref>


== Trophy ==
The trophy is called "Statue of a Woman Playing a Reed Instrument" ({{lang-ko|<U+C0DD><U+D669> <U+BD80><U+B294> <U+C5EC><U+C778><U+C0C1>}}) that was designed by professor Kim Soo-Hyun ({{lang-ko|<U+AE40><U+C218><U+D604>}}).<ref>{{cite web |title=<U+ACE8><U+B4E0> <U+B514><U+C2A4><U+D06C> <U+C0C1> <U+D2B8><U+B85C><U+D53C> |url=http://isplus.joins.com/goldendisk/history/history_trophy.html |publisher=Golden Disk Awards |language=Korean |accessdate=2009-07-16}}</ref>

== Categories ==
Currently there are seven awards which are not restricted by genre, and two awards which are each in [[Hip hop music|hip hop]], [[Trot (music)|trot]].
* '''Grand Prize''' is awarded to the performer of the best of the best album belong to "Records of the Year".
* '''Grand Prize of Digital Releasing''' is awarded to the performer of the best of the best album which was digital released, belong to "Records of the Year".
* '''Records of the Year''' are awarded to the performers of top 10 full albums of the year.
* '''Record Producer of the Year''' is awarded to a [[record producer]] of the year.
* '''Hip Hop Record of the Year''' is awarded to the performer of the [[Hip hop music|hip hop]] album of the year.
* '''Trot Record of the Year''' is awarded to the performer of the [[Trot (music)|trot]] album of the year.
* '''Popularity Awards of the Year''' are awarded to the performers who gained [[popularity]] of the year.
* '''Newbie Awards of the Year''' are awarded to the [[newbie]] performers of the year.
* '''Special Award''' is awarded to the performer or the production team who gained [[popularity]] or outstanding achievement in miscellaneous topics of Korean [[music industry]].

